events.name: Digital Careers Festival
events.description:
January 15 - February 11, 2018

Start your 2018 with a series of classes, workshops and events to help take your passions and career to the next level. 

If you're feeling limited in your current career this is your opportunity to learn from and be inspired by those who become industry leaders and are staying relevant in the rapidly changing working world.

General Assembly organised four weeks focused on UX design, web development, digital marketing, data, and product management.

We're bringing together incredible leaders for collaborative, fun and interactive classes, workshops and events to inspire and motivate you to pursue a career you love!
